flowchart TD
    Start([Student opens app]) --> Login{Logged in?}
    Login -->|No| LoginPage[Login / Register]
    LoginPage --> Auth[Authenticate]
    Auth --> Dashboard[Student Dashboard]

    Login -->|Yes| Dashboard

    Dashboard --> Learn[Browse Learning Path]
    Dashboard --> Match[Match Lobby]
    Dashboard --> Profile[Profile / Achievements]

    Learn --> Unit[Select Unit]
    Unit --> Lesson[Start Lesson]
    Lesson --> Questions[Answer Questions]
    Questions --> LessonResult[Lesson Complete + XP]
    LessonResult --> Dashboard

    Match --> FindOpponent[Find Same-Grade Opponent]
    FindOpponent --> MatchArena[Play 1v1 Match]
    MatchArena --> MatchResult[Match Result + XP]
    MatchResult --> Dashboard

    Profile --> Dashboard
